# Web Development Workshop

In this hands-on session, you'll learn how to build modern web applications using cutting-edge tools and frameworks.

## Topics Covered

- Introduction to Svelte
- Building reactive components
- State management with Stores
- Styling with UnoCSS
- Vite for fast development

## Prerequisites

- Basic knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- A laptop with Node.js installed
- Your favorite code editor

## What to Bring

- Laptop with development environment setup
- Willingness to learn and experiment

## Resources

Participants will receive a GitHub repository with starter code and examples.
